text: Þær þu geseo tordwifel on eorþan upweorfan, ymbfo hine mid twam handum mid his geweorpe.
Wafa mid þinum handum swiþe and cweð þrowa:Remedium facio ad ventris dolorem.
Weorp þonne ofer bæc þone wifel on wege.
Beheald þæt þu ne locige æfter.
Þonne monnes wambe wærce oððe rysle, ymbfoh mid þinum handum þa wambe.
XII monaþ þu meaht swa don æfter þam wifele.
